2164.subject: MLML
2164.descrlong:
MLML 141:Geol Oceanograph-  A study of the structures, physiography, and sediments of the sea bottom and shoreline. Offered through Moss Landing Marine Laboratories (MLML); contact SEP program office for MLML registration procedures. (Offered fall semester.)

(Prereq: Exclude Freshmen and Sophomore and Junior)
